hadiths[164]{hadithnumber,text}:
2313,"Aayat kareema : (يا أيها الذين آمنوا كتب عليكم الصيام كما كتب على الذين من قبلكم) ''aey emaan walo ! tum par roza rakhna farz kiya gaya hai jaisey ke tum se pehley logon par farz kiya gaya tha.'' ki tafseer mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein log jab Isha ki Namaz padh letey to un par khana, peena aur biwiyan haram ho jati thin aur wo agli shaam tak ke liye roze daar ho jatey they. phir (aisey hua ke) eik aadmi apney nafs ki khayanat kar baitha, yani usney apni biwi se ham-bistarii kar li jabkey wo Isha ki Namaz padh chuka tha, aur (sair ho kar) khana bhi nahin khaya tha, tu Allah taala ne chaha ke is amal mein baqi logon ke liye aasani, rukhsat aur nafa paida farma dey, tu Allah taala ne farmaya : (علم الله أنكم كنتم تختانون أنفسكم . ۔) ''Allah taala khoob janta hai ke tum apney nafson ke sath khayanat kartey ho.'' chunanche ye farman isi silsiley mein hai jiskey zariey se Allah taala ne logon ko nafa diya hai aur un ke liye rukhsat (chhoot) aur aasani farma di hai."
2314,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke aadmi jab roza rakhna chahta aur so jata to phir wo agli shaam tak kuchh na kha sakta tha. Hazrat Sirma bin Qais Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) apni zauja (biwi) ke paas aaye jabkey unhoney roza rakha hua tha aur us se kaha : kya terey paas (khaney ki) koi cheez hai? usney kaha : nahin magar main jati hun aur aap ke liye kuchh talash kar laati hun. wo chali gaee aur is beech mein Sirma ki aankh lag gaee. jab wo aai (aur unko sotay huey paya) to kehney lagi : afsos aap ke khasaray par ! chunanche do-pehar na hui ke unhen ghashi aa gaee, aur wo din ko apni zameen mein kaam kya kartey they. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye waqia bataya gaya, iskey baad ye aayat kareema nazil hui : ( أحل لكم ليلة الصيام الرفث إلى نسائكم ( . . . . aapney (من الفجر) tak qirat ki.''rozey ki raat mein tumharey liye apni biwiyon se mubashrat halal ki gaee hai, wo tumhara libas hain aur tum unka libas ho. Allah ko maloom hai ke tum apney nafson ke sath khayanat kar baithtey ho, so usney tum par ruju farmaya aur tumhen maaf kar diya hai. tum ab apni aurton se mubashrat kar saktey ho aur talab karo wo jo Allah ne tumharey liye muqaddar farmaya hai. aur khao piyo yahan tak ke Fajr ke waqt subah ki safed dhaari siyah dhaari se juda nazar aaney lagey.''"
2315,Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke jab ye aayat kareema nazil hui : ''aur jo roza rakhney ki taqat rakhtey hon wo eik miskeen ke khaney ka fidya den.'' to ham mein se jo chahta roza chhod deta aur fidya dena chahta to fidya dey diya karta tha yahan tak ke iskey baad wali aayat utri jisney is (rukhsat) ko mansookh kar diya.
2316,"Ikrima se manqul hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) aayat kareema : (وعلى الذين يطيقونه فدية طعام مسكين) ke silsiley mein farmatey hain ke jo koi eik miskeen ka fidya dena chahta , dey deta tha aur uska roza pura aur kamil samjha jata tha. phir Allah taala ne farmaya : (فمن تطوع خيرا فهو خير له وأن تصوموا خير لكم) ''jo khushi se bhalai karey (miskeen ko khana khilaaey) to ye uskey liye behtar hai aur roza rakhna tumharey liye behtar hai.'' aur farmaya : (فمن شهد منكم الشهر فليصمه ومن كان مريضا أو على سفر فعدة من أيام أخر) ''jo shakhs is mahiney mein hazir ho to usey chahiye ke iskey rozey rakhey. aur jo mareez ho ya safar par ho to wo doosrey dino mein inki ginti puri karey.''"
2317,Ikrima ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) farmatey hain : aayat kareema : (وعلى الذين يطيقونه فدية طعام مسكين) hamila aur doodh pilaney wali ke haq mein mohkam hai. (mansookh nahin hai.)
2318,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke aayat kareema : (وعلى الذين يطيقونه فدية طعام مسكين) ki tafseer mein unhoney kaha ke badi umr ke boodhey mard aur aurat ke liye rukhsat (chhoot) hai ke bawajood rozey ki taqat ke iftaar kar saktey hain. wo her din ke badley eik miskeen ko khana khila diya karen. isi tarah hamila aur doodh pilaney wali aurton ko jab andesha ho. (to wo bhi iftaar kar sakti hain.) Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : maqsad ye hai ke jab unhen apney bachchey ke baarey mein (bimari ya kamzori waghaira ka ( andesha ho to iftaar kar sakti hain aur iskey badley khana khila diya karen.
2319,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham ummee ummat hain, ham likhna nahin jantey aur na (daqeeq) hisab kar saktey hain. (aapney dono haathon ki dason ungliyan phela kar isharay se farmaya) mahina aisey hota hai aur aisey hota hai aur aisey hota hai.'' aur teesri baar mein Sulaiman bin Harab ne apni eik ungli band kar li. yani untees din aur tees din."
2320,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mahina untees din ka (bhi) hota hai. so chaand dekhay baghair na rozey shuru karo aur na dekhay baghair khatam karo. agar badal ke baais nazar na aaye to us mahiney ke tees din ka andaza laga lo.'' chunanche jab Shoban ki unteesween taareekh hoti to Hazrat Abdullah bin umr ke liye chaand dekha jata. agar nazar aa jata to behtar aur agar dikhai na deta aur nazar na aaney mein koi badal ya ghubar bhi haael (rukawat) na hota to wo roza na rakhtay. lekin agar fiza mein koi badal ya ghubar haael hota to wo roza rakh letey. raawi ne bayan kiya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) logon ke sath hi roza chhodtey aur hisab ke dar pai na hotey."
2321,Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez ne ehle-Basra ki taraf likha ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees pahunchi hai jaisey ke mazkura baala ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki hadees hai. us mein ye izafa hai : '' behtareen andaza ye hai ke agar ham ne Shoban ka chaand falan falan din dekha to roza inshaAllah falan din ka hoga siwaey iske ke log us se pehley hi chaand dekh lein .''
2322,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ( Ramazan mein) untees untees rozey bahut ziyada rakhey hain aur tees tees kam."
2323,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Bakra apney walid sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''Eid ke dono mahiney yani Ramazan aur zul-hijja kam nahin hotey hain. ''"
2324,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai) ye taweel hadees ka eik hissa hai) ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Eidul-fitr isi din hai jab tum iftaar karo aur Eide-qurban isi din hai jab tum qurbani karo. sara maidan Arafat waquf ki jagah hai aur sara Mina jaey qurbani hai, Makka ke tamam raastey qurbani ki jagah hain aur sara Muzdalfa waquf ki jagah hai.''"
2325,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Shoban ki taareekhon ki itni nigehdasht rakhtey they ke doosrey mahinon mein itni nigehdasht na rakhtey they. phir chaand dekh kar Ramazan ke rozey rakhney shuru kartey agar kabhi (Shoban ki untees taareekh ko) matla abr-aalood hota, to tees din purey kartey aur phir rozey rakhna shuru kartey."
2326,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mahina shuru honey se pehley rozey mat rakho yahan tak ke chaand dekh lo ya (tees ki) ginti puri kar lo, phir rozey rakhtey jao yahan tak ke chaand dekh lo ya ( tees ki) ginti puri kar lo . Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke us riwayat ko Sufiyan waghera ne Mansoor sey, unhoney Rabai sey, unhoney eik sahabi se bayan kya hai aur is sanad mein) sahabi ke naam ( Huzefa ki saraahat nahin hai."
2327,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mahina (Ramazan ( shuru honey se pehley eik do din ke rozey mat rakho (istiqbali rozey mat rakho) siwaey iske ke koi shakhs us din ka roza rakha karta ho. chaand dekh kar rozey shuru karo, phir rakhtey jao yahan tak ke) shawwaal ka ( chaand dekh lo. agar uskey dikhai deney mein koi badal ( waghera) rukawat ho to tees ki ginti puri kar lo aur phir rozey moquf kar do . aur mahina untees din ka ( bhi) hota hai. '' Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : us riwayat ko Hatim bin abi sagheera , Shoba aur Hasan bin saleh ne samaak se usi (mazkura baala ( riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya hai magar '' rozey moquf kar do '' ka jumla unki riwayat mein nahin hai. Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ''Hatim bin abi sagheera'' ka nasab yun hai : '' Hatim bin Muslim ibne-abi sagheera '' aur '' Abu-Sagheera '' Hatim ka sotela baap tha."
2328,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs se puchha : ''kya to ne Shoban ke aakhir mein koi roza rakha hai? '' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''jab ( Ramazan ke) rozey purey kar lo to eik din roza rakh lena .'' ( Sabit ya Saeed Jariri dono mein se kisi ( eik ne bayan kya ke '' do din .''
2329,"Abu-Azhar Mughira bin Farwa se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) dere-Mis-hal mein logon ko khutba deney ke liye khadey huey jo ke baabe-Hims ke paas hai. unhoney kaha : logo! ham ne (Shoban ka ( chaand falan-falan din dekha tha, main (chaand honey sey) pehley rozey shuru kar raha hun, jo aisa karna chahey kar ley. phir Malik bin Hubaira al-Sabi unke samney khada hua aur kaha : aey Muawiya ! is silsiley mein aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kuch suna hai ya ye aapki apni raey hai? kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''mahiney mein rozey rakha karo aur uskey aakhir mein bhi.'' (doosra tarjama : Ramazan ke rozey rakho aur uskey awwal mein bhi. yani aakhir Shoban mein.)"
2330,Janab abu-Amr Auzaai bayan kartey hain ke) سره (ke maani '' ibtadaaey mahina '' hain.
2331,Janab Saeed bin Abdul-Azeez bayan kartey hain ke) سره (ke maani '' ibtadaaey mahina '' hain. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : kuch ehle-lughat uska tarjama '' wast '' aur kaee '' aakhir mahina '' bhi kartey hain.
2332,"Janab kuraib kehtey hain ke (Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki walida) Umme-Fazal binte-Haris (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey Shaam mein Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja . chunanche main shaam aaya aur wahan unka kaam mukammal kya, aur Ramazan ka chaand nazar aa gaya jabkey main abhi shaam hi mein tha. ham ne Juma ki raat ko chaand dekha . phir mahiney ke aakhir mein main Madiney wapis pahuncha to Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne mujh se haal ahwaal puchey aur chaand ka zikr kya ke tum ne usey kab dekha tha? maine kaha : maine usey Juma ki raat ko dekha tha? unhoney kaha : kya tum ne khud dekha tha? maine kaha : haan, aur doosrey logon ne bhi dekha tha aur phir sab ne rozey rakhey aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi roza rakha. unhoney kaha magar ham ne usey haftey ki raat ko dekha tha aur ham rozey rakhengey aur purey tees karengey (apni ruiyat ke mutabiq) ya chaand dekh lein. maine kaha : kya aap Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke chaand dekhney aur rozey rakhney par kifaayat nahin karengey? unhoney kaha : nahin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen aisey hi hukm diya hai."
2333,"Hasan (Basri) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs jo kisi shehar mein ho aur usney somwar ka roza rakha ho, phir do aadmi gawahi den ke unhoney itwaar ki raat (haftey ki shaam) ko chaand dekha hai. to Hasan ne kaha : ye aadmi aur uskey shehar waley us din ka roza qaza na keren siwaey iske ke unhen b-khubi ilm ho ke musalmanon ke shehron mein se kisi shehar walon ne itwaar ka roza rakha hai, tab ye uski qaza karen."
2334,Janab Sila bayan kartey hain ke ham Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir they aur wo din mashkook tha ( chaand honey ki khabar wazeh na hui thi ( to bakri ka gosht pesh kya gaya. pas majlis mein se kuch log eik taraf ho gaey . Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jisney is din ka roza rakha hai usney abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki hai.
2335,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ramazan se eik do din pehley rozey mat rakho magar jo koi shakhs kisi din ka roza rakhta raha ho to wo rakh ley.''"
2336,"ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq bayan karti hain ke aap saal mein kisi mahiney ke purey rozey na rakhtey they magar Shoban mein, ke usey Ramazan ke sath mila detey they."
2337,"Ibad bin kaseer Madiney aaye aur Janab Ala bin Abdur-Rehman ki majlis mein aa gaey. pas Ibaad ne Ala ka haath pakad kar unhen khada kar diya phir kaha : aey Allah ! ye shakhs apney baap se wo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Shoban aadha guzar jaey to roza na rakho .'' phir Ala ne kaha : ya Allah ! merey walid ( Abdur-Rehman ( ne mujhey Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Sauri , shabal bin Ala, Abu-Umais aur Zuhair bin Muhammad bin Ala se bayan kartey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : Abdur-Rehman (bin Mehdi ( ye riwayat bayan nahin kya kartey they, maine Imam Ahmed se puchha kyon ? to unhoney kaha : kyonkey unke paas ye hadees thi ke '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Shoban ko Ramazan ke sath mila detey they. '' aur is riwayat mein uskey khilaf marwi (bayan) hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : merey nazdik us mein koi mukhalifat nahin hai. Ala ke ilawa usey aur koi riwayat nahin karta aur wo bhi apney baap se riwayat karta hai."
2338,"Husain bin Haris Jadli.... Qais ke qabila Jadila se hain.... bayan kartey hain ke ameere-Makka ne khutba diya aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham se ehad liya ke ham chaand dekh kar hajj ke arkaan ada karen. agar ham khud na dekh saken aur do aadil gawah gawahi dey den to ham unki gawahi par hajj kar lein .) abu-Malik kehtey hain : ( maine Husain bin Haris se puchha : ameer Makka kon tha? usney kaha : mujhey maloom nahin. baad mein wo mujhey dobara mila to bataya ke wo ( ameer ( Haris bin Haatib they, yani Muhammad bin Haatib ke bhai . phir ameer ne kaha : bila-shuba tum mein wo shakhsiyat mojud hai jo Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq mujh se ziyada ba-khabar hai, is baat ki shahadat usi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se di hai aur apney haath se eik aadmi ki taraf ishara kya. Husain ne bataya . . . . . maine apney pehlu mein bethey huey eik shakhs se puchha : ye aadmi kon hai jiski taraf ameer ne ishara kya hai? to usney kaha : ye Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) hain aur usney sach kaha ke ye Allah ke mutalliq us se ziyada jantey they ( ehkam shariyat ( to Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen isi baat ka hukm diya hai."
2339,"Rabae bin Harash, as-haab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se kisi se riwayat kartey hain ke Ramazan ke aakhiri din ke mutalliq logon ka ikhtilaf ho gaya. to do erab aaye aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney Allah ki gawahi di ( qasmen uthaeyn (ke unhoney kal shaam ko chaand dekha hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ko hukm diya ke roza iftaar kar lein. aur khalaf bin Hisham ki riwayat mein mazeed ye hai ke aapney farmaya : ''agley din subh ko (eid padhney ke liye) eid gaah jaeyn .''"
2340,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke eik eiraab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : maine chaand dekha hai. Hasan bin Ali ne apni hadees mein saraahat kartey huey kaha ke murad hai Ramazan ka chaand . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya to ( La-ilaah-illallah ( ki gawahi deta hai? '' usney kaha : haan . aapney puchha : kya to gawahi deta hai ke Muhammad Allah ke Rasool hain, usney kaha : haan . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Bilal ! logon mein aelan kar do ke subh roza rakhen .''"
2341,"Ikrima bayan kartey hain ke Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ko eik baar Ramazan ke chaand mein shak ho gaya. pas unhoney irada kya ke na qiyam keren aur na roza rakhen. to Harra ki taraf se eik eiraab aaya. usney gawahi di ke usney chaand dekha hai. usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya gaya, aapney farmaya : ''kya to (La-ilaah-illallah Muhammad Rasulullah) ki gawahi deta hai? ''usney kaha : haan aur shahadat di ke usney chaand dekha hai. tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal ko hukm diya ke logon mein aelan kar do ke raat ko qiyam keren aur) subh ko) roza rakhen. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko eik jamaat ne b-waasta samaak, Ikrima se mursal riwayat kya hai. aur qiyam ka zikr Hammad bin Salma ke ilawa kisi ne nahin kya."
2342,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke logon ne chaand dekhney ki koshish ki . pas maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khabar di ke maine dekh liya hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne roza rakha aur logon ko roza rakhney ka hukm farmaya.
2343,"Hazrat Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamarey aur ehle-kitab ke rozey mein farq, sehri ke khaney ka hai.''"
2344,Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Ramazan mein sehri ke liye bulaya aur farmaya : ''aao! Mubarak khana ( غداء ( kha lo.''
2345,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khajoor momin ki behtareen sehri hai. ''"
2346,Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba diya aur bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Bilal ki Azan tumhen tumhari sehri se hergiz na rokey aur na ufuq ki safedi ( jo ke sidhi ooper ko chadhti hai) yahan tak ke atraaf mein phailney lagey .''
2347,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Bilal ki Azan tum mein se kisi ko sehri khaney se hergiz na rokey . bila-shuba wo Azan kehta hai. ... . ya kaha, Nida deta hai. ... . taake tumhara Namaz padhney wala ruk jaey (tahajjud sey) aur soney wala jaag jaey. aur Fajr ( Fajr saadiq ( wo nahin jo is tarah se zahir ho. ... . Musaddad ne kaha : raawi hadees Yahya ne apni dono hatheliyan mila kar unko ooncha karkey dikhlaaya ( jo oonchi aur lambi roshni awwal waqt hoti hai wo subh nahin) aapney farmaya : ''jab tak is tarah zahir na ho.'' aur Yahya ne apni shahadat ki dono ungliyan atraaf mein phela kar isharay se samjhaya ."
2348,"Qais bin Talaq apney walid se bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (raat ko) khao aur piyo, ooper chadhney wali safedi tumhen us se na rokey, yahan tak ke ufuq ke atraaf mein surkhi phailni shuru ho jaey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ''is riwayat mein ehle-Yamama munfarid hain.''"
2349,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke jab ye aayat karima nazil hui : حتى يتبين لكم الخيط الأبيض من الخيط الأسود (tum khatey peetey raho) yahan tak ke subh ka safed dhaaga siyah dhaagey se numaya ho jaey.'' to maine do rassiyan le-lin, eik safed aur dusri siyah aur unhen apney takiye ke nichey rakh liya . main unhen dekhta raha magar wo merey liye numaya aur wazeh na huin . maine ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr ki to aap hansay aur farmaya : '' tera takiya to bahut lamba chauda hai. us se murad to raat aur din hai. '' Usman ke alfaz ye hain.'' us se murad to raat ki siyahi aur din ki safedi hai. ''"
2350,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jab koi Azan (Fajr) suney aur bartan uskey haath mein ho to usey rakhey nahin balke apni zarurat puri kar ley.''
2351,"Janab Aasim apney walid Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab udhar se raat aa jaey ( mashriq ki janib sey) aur udhar se din chala jaey ( maghrib se .'' ( Musaddad ne mazeed kaha : '' aur Suraj ghuroob ho jaey to rozey daar ke liye iftaar ka waqt ho gaya .''"
2352,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke) eik safar mein) ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath gaey jabkey aap rozey se they. jab Suraj ghuroob ho gaya to aapney farmaya .'' aey Bilal ! utro aur hamarey liye sattu gholo .'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! zara shaam ho leney dijiye . aapney farmaya : '' utro aur hamarey liye sattu gholo .'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! abhi to din hai. aapney farmaya : '' utro aur hamarey liye sattu gholo .'' chunanche Bilal utrey , sattu gholaa aur phir aapney nosh kya aur farmaya : ''jab dekho ke udhar se raat ho gaee hai to bila-shuba rozey daar ke liye iftaar ka waqt ho gaya .'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni ungli se mashriq ki taraf ishara farmaya."
2353,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se naqal kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' deen us waqt tak ghalib rahega jab tak log iftaar kerney mein jaldi kartey rahengey kyonkey yahood w nasara takheer se iftaar kartey hain. ''"
2354,"Janab abu-Atiya (Malik bin Aamir) se marwi (bayan) hai, kehtey hain ke main aur Masruq ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey . ham ne kaha : aey ummul-momenin ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab mein se do hazraat ka amal kuch is tarah hai ke un mein se eik iftaar kerney aur Namaz (maghrib) padhney mein jaldi karta hai aur doosra iftaar aur Namaz mein (qadrey) takheer karta hai. unhoney puchha : iftaar aur Namaz mein jaldi kon karta hai? ham ne kaha : wo Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) hain. unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi aisey hi kya kartey they."
2355,"Janab Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) (ye Rubab ke chacha hain) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ne roza rakha ho to chahiye ke khajoor se iftaar karey. agar khajoor na paey to pani se iftaar karey, bila-shuba pani paak kerney wala hai.''"
2356,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se pehley taza khajuron se roza iftaar farmatey, agar taza khajuren na hotin to khushk khajoor kha letey, ye bhi na hotin, to pani ke chand ghoont pi liya kartey they."
2357,"Marwan bin Salim Muqaffa kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko dekha ke wo dadhi ko apni mutthi mein letey aur us se jo badhi hui hoti usey kaat daltey . aur bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab roza iftaar kartey to ye dua padhtey they : ذهب الظمأ وابتلت العروق وثبت الأجر إن شاء الله ''piyas bujh gaee, ragein tar ho gaeen aur Allah ne chaha to ajr bhi Sabit ho gaya.''"
2358,Janab Muaz bin Zohra (Taabai) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) iftaar ke waqt ye dua padhtey they : ( اللهم لك صمت وعلى رزقك أفطرت ) ''aey Allah ! maine terey liye roza rakha aur terey hi rizq par khol raha hun. ''
2359,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Ramazan mein ham ne eik din badal ki wajeh se roza khol liya , phir Suraj nikal aaya . Abu-Usama kehtey hain ke maine Hisham se puchha : to kya unhen qaza deney ka hukm diya gaya tha? kaha : bhala us se koi chaara bhi hai?"
2360,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rozon mein wisaal kerney se mana farmaya. Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap to wisaal kartey hain? aapney farmaya : ''main tumhari tarah nahin hun. be-shak mujhey khilaya pilaya jata hai. ''
2361,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum log ( rozon mein) wisaal mat karo, aur jo koi wisaal karna chahey , to sahar tak kar ley.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aap to wisaal kartey hain? aapney farmaya : ''main tumhari tarah nahin hun, bila-shuba eik khilaney wala hai jo mujhey khilata hai aur pilaney wala hai jo mujhey pilata hai.''"
2362,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs jhoot aur be hooda bolna aur jhoot par amal karna na chodey, tu Allah taala ko uskey khaney-peeney ke chhod deney ki zarurat nahin hai.'' Ahmed bin Yunus ne kaha : mujhey iski sanad ibne-abi Zi-ib ne aur ye hadees us aadmi ne samjhai jo uskey pehlu mein betha hua tha, jo ghaaliban uska bhai tha."
2363,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi rozey se ho to kisi qism ki fohsh baat ya jihalat ka kaam na karey. agar koi doosra us se jhagdey ya gaali galoch dey to usey chahiye ke keh dey mein rozey se hun, maine roza rakha hua hai.''"
2364,"Janab Ubaidullah bin Aamir bin Rabeea apney walid (Aamir bin Rabeea) se riwayat kartey hain, unka kehna hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko miswak kartey huey dekha, halanke aap rozey se they. Musaddad ne mazeed yun kaha : maine aap ko be shumar dafa (miswak kartey) dekha ."
2365,"Janab abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman kisi sahabi se riwayat kartey hain ke maine dekha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke saal apney safar mein Sahaba ko roza iftaar kerney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : ''dushman ke muqabley ke liye quwat hasil karo.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khud roza rakha. abu-Bakar ne kaha : mujhey hadees bayan kerney waley ne bataya : tehqiq maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko maqam Araj mein dekha aap rozey se they aur piyas ya garmi ki wajeh se apney sar par pani dal rahey they."
2366,"Hazrat Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(wuzu kartey huey) naak mein khoob pani chadhaao, siwaye uskey ke rozey se ho.''"
2367,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' seengi laganey aur lagwaaney wala roza kholney wala ho gaya. Sheban ne apni hadees mein kaha : mujhey abu-Qulaba ne khabar di , usko abu-Asmaa al-Raji ne hadees bayan ki ke Soban maula Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko khabar di ke usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha."
2368,Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) ka kehna hai ke eik baar main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ja raha tha aur mazkura baala ki manind zikr kya.
2369,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baqee ke qarib eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey aur wo seengi lagwa raha tha, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mera haath thaamey huey they aur Ramazan ki atthara taarikh thi, aapney farmaya : ''seengi laganey aur lagwaaney wala (dono) roza kholney waley ho gaey . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Khalid al-Khada ne ( bhi) abu-Qulaba se Ayub ki sanad se riwayat kya hai."
2370,Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) maula Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' seengi laganey wala aur lagwaaney wala (dono) muftir (roza kholney waley) ho gaey .''
2371,Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain aapney farmaya : '' seengi laganey wala aur lagwaaney wala muftir ( roza kholney waley (ho gaey . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ibn Soban ne bhi apney walid se Mak-hool ki sanad se iski manind riwayat kya hai.
2372,"Ikrima Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rozey ki haalat mein seengi lagwai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : is riwayat ko Wuhaib bin Khalid ne Ayub se apni sanad se usi ke misl riwayat kya hai, neez Jaafar bin Rabeea aur Hisham bin Hassaan, Ikrima se wo Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se usi ke misl riwayat kartey hain."
2373,Muqsim Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rozey aur ehram ki haalat mein seengi lagwai hai.
2374,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Laila kehtey hain ke mujh se eik sahabi ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba par shafqat farmatey huye, unhen seengi lagwaaney aur rozon mein wisaal kerney se mana kya magar aapney un dono ko haram nahin kya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap to sahar tak wisaal kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''main sahar tak wisaal karta hun aur mera rab mujhey khilata pilata hai. ''"
2375,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ham rozey daar ko seengi isliye nahin lagwaaney detey they ke kahin usey mashaqqat na ho.
2376,"eik sahabi se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey qai aa jaey ya (neend mein) ehtilaam ho jaey ya jo seengi lagwaaey, to uska roza nahin toot-ta.''"
2377,"Abdur-Rehman bin Noman apney walid sey, wo dada sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney hukm diya ke sotey waqt kastoori mila surma istemal kya jaey aur farmaya : '' roze daar us se perhez karey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke mujhey Imam Yahya bin moayan ne kaha ye surmey wali hadees munkar hai."
2378,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq riwayat hai ke wo rozey ki haalat mein surma lagaya kartey they.
2379,Janab Aamash kehtey hain (ye sighaar taabein mein se hain) maine apney ehle-ilm doston (fuqha w muhaddesin) mein se kisi ko nahin paya ke rozey daar ke liye surmey ko makruh samajhtey hon. aur Ibrahim Nakhai ijazat detey they ke rozey daar Elwa ko bator surma istimal karey.
2380,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kisi ko qai aa jaey jabkey wo rozey se ho to us par koi qaza nahin hai, lekin agar wo qasdan qai karey to qaza dey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke us riwayat ko Hafs bin Ghiyas ne bhi Hisham se usi ke misl riwayat kya hai."
2381,Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qai ki aur roza tod dala. (Maadan kehtey hain ke) phir Hazrat Soban maula Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se dimashq ki masjid mein meri mulaqat hui to maine un se kaha : Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qai ki aur roza tod dala tha. kaha ke unhoney sahih kaha hai aur maine hi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye wuzu ka pani undela tha.
2382,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein bosa ley liya kartey they aur rozey ki haalat mein biwi ke sath let bhi jatey they, lekin aap apney jazbaat par khoob zabt rakhney waley they."
2383,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maahe-Ramazan mein (biwiyon ka ( bosa ley liya kartey they.
2384,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mera bosa liya kartey they jabkey aap rozey se hotey aur main bhi .
2385,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine khushi mein aa kar (biwi ka ( bosa ley liya jabkey main rozey se tha. phir maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! main aaj eik bahut bada kaam kar betha hun ke rozey ki haalat mein bosa ley liya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bhala agar tum rozey ki haalat mein kulli kar lo to?'' Esa bin Hammad ki riwayat mein hai. maine kaha : koi harj nahin. aapney farmaya : ''to us mein bhi koi harj nahin.''
2386,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unka bosa ley letey jabkey wo rozey se hotey aur unki zaban choostey . ibn-Eirabi kehtey hain ke mujhey Imam Abu-Dawud se ye baat pahunchi hai ke ye sanad sahih nahin hai.
2387,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke eik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha ke roza daar shakhs biwi ke sath letey ya na? aapney usko ijazat di. phir doosra aaya aur usney bhi aap se yehi masla puchha . aapney usko mana farma diya. darasal aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jis ko ijazat di , wo boodha tha aur jis ko mana farmaya , wo jawan tha."
2388,"ummahatul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha aur umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo bayan karti hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subh ko junbi ho kar uthtey .... . Abdullah azrami ne apni riwayat mein kaha ke Ramazan mein .....jimaa ki bina par na ke ehtilaam se aur phir roza rakh letey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke یصبح جنبا في رمضان ka lafz bahut kam raawi zikr kartey hain. (sahih) hadees ke lafz ye hain : أن النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم كان يصبح جنبا وهو صائم ''nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) janabat ki haalat mein subh kartey aur aap roza rakhey huey hotey.''"
2389,ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha jabkey aap darwazey par khadey they : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main bahaalate-janabat subh karta hun aur roza bhi rakhna chahta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main bhi (kabhi-kabhi) subh ko janabat ki haalat mein uthta hun aur rozey ka irada hota hai to ghusl kar leta hun aur roza rakhta hun.'' wo aadmi kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool! aap to hamari manind nahin hain. Allah azz-w-jall ne aap ki agli pichli tamam taqseerat maaf farmaai hui hain. us par aap ghazabnaak ho gaey aur farmaya : ''qasam Allah ki ! main yaqinan tum mein sab se ziyada Allah se darney wala hun aur ittiba ke laaiq aamaal se bahut ziyada aagah hun. ''
2390,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : main to maara gaya. aapney puchha : ''kya hua?'' usney kaha : main Ramazan main apni biwi se ham-bistar ho betha hun. ... . aapney puchha : ''kya to taqat rakhta hai ke eik gardan azad kar sakey ?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''kya to himmat rakhta hai ke do maah mutawatir rozey rakhey ?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''kya tujhey taqat hai ke 60 miskeenon ko khana khila sakey?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''beth jao.'' chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik tokraa laya gaya, us mein khajuren thin. aapney us se farmaya : '' unko sadqa kar do.'' wo kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Madiney ki dono pathreeli zaminon ke beech ham se ziyada aur koi faqir nahin hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans padey yahan tak ke aap ke agley daant dikhai deney lagey . aapney farmaya : '' ghar walon hi ko khila do . Musaddad ne apni riwayat mein kaha ke aap ke nokeeley daant nazar aaney lagey ."
2391,"Janab Zohri ne ye hadees usi mazkura maani mein bayan ki aur mazeed kaha : ye usi aadmi ke liye rukhsat thi aaj agar koi ye kaam kar bethey to kaffaarey se chaara nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : is riwayat ko Leis bin Saad, Auzaai, Mansoor bin Motamir aur Irak bin Malik ne Sufiyan bin Uena ki manind bayan kya. Auzaai ne apni riwayat mein ye ziyada kya : ''aur Allah se istighfar bhi kar.''"
2392,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aadmi ne Ramazan mein roza tod liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya ke eik gardan Azad karey ya do maah mutawatir rozey rakhey ya 60 miskeenon ko khana khilaaey. usney kaha : main (kisi ki bhi) taqat nahin rakhta . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : '' beth jao .'' phir aap ke paas eik tokraa laya gaya , us mein khajuren thin , aapney farmaya : ''ye ley jao aur sadqa karo .'' wo kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujh se badh kar aur koi mohtaj nahin hai. to aap hans padey yahan tak ke aap ke nokeeley daant nazar aaney lagey aur us se farmaya : ''jao kha lo . Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ibne-Juraij ne Zohri se bilfaaz Imam Malik riwayat kya aur kaha ke '' eik aadmi ne roza tod liya .'' aur aapney us se farmaya : ''ya to eik gardan azad karo ya do maah rozey rakho ya saath miskeenon ko khana khilao .''"
2393,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya jisney Ramazan ke din mein roza tod liya tha, aur mazkura baala hadees bayan ki . raawi ne kaha : phir aap ke paas eik tokraa laya gaya , us mein khajoor thi taqreeban pandarah saa . ... . us riwayat mein hai. ... . aapney us se farmaya : '' to aur terey ghar waley ye kha lein aur to eik din ka roza rakh aur Allah se istighfar kar .''"
2394,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Ramazan main eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas masjid mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main to jal gaya , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''kya hua ?'' usney kaha : maine apni biwi se jima kar liya hai. aapney farmaya : '' sadqa karo .'' kehney laga : Allah ki qasam ! merey paas koi chiz nahin aur na meri ye himmat hai. aapney farmaya : '' beth jao .'' wo beth gaya. wo usi haalat mein tha ke eik aadmi apna gadha chalatey huey aaya, us par tuaam tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kahan hai wo jo abhi keh raha tha mein jal gaya ?'' wo khada ho gaya. aapney farmaya : ''ye sadqa kar do .'' kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ( apney ilawa ( doosron par ? qasam Allah ki ! ham bhookey hain, hamarey paas kuch nahin hai. aapney farmaya : '' ( jao ( kha lo .''"
2395,Ibad bin Abdullah Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se is qissey mein bayan kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik tokraa laya gaya us mein bees saa ( khajoor ( thi.
2396,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Ramazan mein roza tod dey , baghair kisi rukhsat ke jo Allah ne di hai to zamana bhar ke rozey bhi uski talafi nahin kar sakengey.''"
2397,"Imaara bin Umair ne ibn Mutwis se riwayat kya aur kaha : main ibn Mutwis se mila to usney mujhey apney walid sey, usney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees bayan ki jaisey ke ibn kaseer aur Suleman ki riwayat ( ooper mazkur hui ( hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Sufiyan aur Shoba ke shagrid un se bayan kerney mein mukhtalif hain. kuch '' ibn Mutwis '' kehtey hain aur kuch '' Abu-Mutwis.''"
2398,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine roza rakha hua tha aur bhool kar kha pi betha hun. aapney farmaya : ''Allah ne tumhen khilaya aur pilaya hai. ''
2399,Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mujh par Ramazan ke rozey baqi hotey aur main unki qaza na kar paati thi ke Shoban aa jata .
2400,"Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi faut ho jaey aur uskey zimmey rozey rehtey hon to uska wali uski taraf se rozey rakhey . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ye masla nazar ki soorat mein hai aur Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal ka bhi yehi qol hai."
2401,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka qol hai ke jab koi shakhs Ramazan mein bimar hua aur phir faut ho gaya aur rozey na rakh saka ho to uski taraf se khana khila diya jaey, us par qaza nahin hai. agar usney nazar maani thi to uska wali qaza dey ."
2402,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Hamza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main tasalsul se rozey rakha karta hun, to kya safar mein roza rakha karun ? aapney farmaya : '' chaho to rakh lo aur agar chaho to iftaar kar lo .''"
2403,"Janab Hamza bin Muhammad bin Hamza Aslami bayan kartey hain ke uskey walid ne uskey dada se bayan kya (ke Hamza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine sawari ke janwer rakhey huey hain. mera kaam unhi se mutalliq hai, safar mein rehta hun, janwer kiraaey par chalata hun aur kabhi-kabhi ye Ramazan ka mahina bhi aa jata hai aur main apney andar taqat paata hun aur jawan hun. aey Allah ke Rasool ! main rozey muakhkhar kerney ki bajaey rakh lena ziyada aasan samajhta hun, warna merey zimmey reh jaeyngey to aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey roza rakhney mein ziyada ajr hai ya iftaar kerney mein ? aapney farmaya : '' Hamza ! jo chaho kar saktey ho.''"
2404,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madiney se Makka ki taraf rawana huey yahan tak ke maqam asfaan par pahunch gaey, phir aapney bartan mangwaya aur usey apney munh ki taraf buland kya taake log aap ko dekh lein (ke aap iftaar kar rahey hain (aur ye Ramazan ka waqia hai. chunanche ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) farmaya kartey they ke bila-shuba Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne roza rakha hai aur chhoda bhi, so jo chahey rakh ley aur jo chahey iftaar kar ley ."
2405,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, unhoney kaha : ham ne Ramazan mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar kya to ham mein se kuch ne roza rakha aur kuch ne na rakha . chunanche rozey daaron ne chhodney walon par ya chhodney walon ne rozey daaron par koi aeb na lagaya ."
2406,"qaza bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke wo logon ke sawaalon ke jawab dey rahey they aur log un par jhukey huey they. maine bheed ke chhat janey ka intizar kiya. jab wo akeley ho gaey to maine un se safar mein Ramazan ke rozon ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha ke Fateh Makka ke saal ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey . aapney rozey rakhey , to ham bhi rakhtey rahey yahan tak ke eik manzil par pahunchey , to aapney farmaya : ''tum log ab apney dushman ke qarib aagey ho aur iftaar karna tumharey liye ziyada quwat ka baais hai. ''to ham mein se kuch ne roza rakha aur kuch ne iftaar kar liya. phir ham chaley aur eik manzil par padaaw kiya to aapney farmaya : ''tum log subah ko apney dushman ke muqabil aaney waley ho aur iftaar karna tumharey liye ziyada quwat ka baais hai, so iftaar kar lo. ''chunanche ye hukm Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se taakeedi tha. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey yaad hai ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath is se pehley rozey rakhey hain aur baad mein bhi."
2407,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dekha eik shakhs ko saya kiya ja raha hai aur log us par azdahaam (bheed) kiye huey hain. (rozey aur garmi ke baais wo ghash kha gaya tha) to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safar mein roza rakhna koi neki ka kaam nahin hai.''
2408,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Ka'bi) se riwayat hai aur ye bani Abdullah bin Kab ke khandan se hain jo ke bani Qushair ke bhai they. ... .) Anas bin Malik jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khaadim they wo khazraji Ansari hain. ...) (kaha) ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sawaron ne ham par hamla kar diya to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha aur (dekha ke) aap kuchh tanaawul farma (kha) rahey hain. aapney farmaya : ''aao ! baitho aur hamarey is tuaam (khaane) mein se kuchh kha lo.'' maine arz kiya : main rozey se hun. aapney farmaya : ''baith jao main tumhen Namaz aur rozey ke mutalliq batata hun. Allah ne musafir se aadhi Namaz aur roza maaf farma diya hai aur doodh pilaney wali aur hamila aurat se bhi roza maaf kar diya hai.'' qasam Allah ki ! aapney un dono ka zikr farmaya tha ya kisi eik ka. bayan kartey hain ke mujhey (baad mein) bahut afsos hua ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khaney mein se kyon na khaya. (kyonkey aap ke sath mil kar khana sa'adat aur baaise barkat tha aur roza nafl mehaz (sirf).)
2409,Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ham eik baar sakht garmi mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath kisi ghazwey ke liye rawana huey . garmi itni thi ke har eik apna haath ya apni hatheli apney sar par rakhey huey tha. aur ham mein se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abdullah bin Rawaha ke siwa aur koi rozey daar na tha.
2410,"Janab Sanan bin Salma bin Mohbiq Hazli apney walid se bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiskey paas sawari ho ke (usey aaram se manzil par pahuncha dey aur) pet bhar kar khana waghaira mil jaey to usey chahiye ke Ramazan ke rozey rakhey, jahan bhi aa jaey.''"
2411,"Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey Ramazan aa pahunchey aur wo safar mein ho to . ... .'' aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani hadees bayan ki."
2412,"Ubaid bin Jabr kehtey hain ke main sahibe Rasool Hazrat Abu-Basra Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha. ham maahe Ramazan mein fistaat se kashti mein sawar huey. jab langar utha liya gaya to unhen unka subah ka khana pesh kiya gaya. Jaafar bin Musafir ne apni riwayat mein kaha. abhi gharon se door bhi na huey they ke unhoney apna dastar khuwan talab kiya aur kaha ke qarib ho jao. main (ubaid) ne kaha : kya aap gharon ko nahin dekh rahey? Janab Abu-Basra ne kaha : kya tum sunnate Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bachna chahte ho? Jaafar ne bayan kiya, chunanche unhoney khana khaya."
2413,Mansoor Kalbi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Dahiya bin Khalifa Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) eik baar Ramazan mein dimashq ki eik basti se rawana huey aur is qadr fasley par gaey jo Aqba se fistaat tak ke beech hai aur in mein teen meel ka fasla hai. phir unhoney iftaar kar liya aur unke sath logon ne bhi kar liya jabkey kuchh doosron ne iftaar kerney ko napasand kiya. phir jab apni basti mein wapis aaye to kaha : qasam Allah ki ! maine aaj eik aisi baat dekhi hai jiska mujhey guman bhi nahin tha ke eik qaum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke as-haab ki sunnat se aeraz karegi (bachegi). wo ye baat un logon ke baarey mein keh rahey they jo rozey se rahey (aur iftaar na kiya) phir is moqe par (dua kartey huey) kaha : aey Allah ! mujhey apni taraf utha ley.
2414,Janab Naafe (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ghaba ki taraf tashrif ley jatey to us safar mein na iftaar kartey aur na qasr.
2415,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs hergiz yun na kahe ke maine sara Ramazan rozey rakhey aur maine sarey Ramazan ka qiyam kiya.'' kehtey hain mujhey maloom nahin aapney neki ko numaya karna makruh jana ya ye batana chaha ke banda is dauran mein lazimi taur par sota bhi raha hai. (to sara Ramazan Roza aur qiyam kis tarah ho gaya?)
2416,Abu-Ubaid kehtey hain ke main eid ke roz Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan hazir tha. aapney pehley Namaz padhaai phir khutba diya aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (eid ke) in do dino mein rozey se mana farmaya hai. qurbani ke din mein tum apni qurbaniyon ke gosht khatey ho aur eidul fitr mein tum rozon se farigh hotey ho.
2417,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do dino ke rozon se mana farmaya hai, yani eidul fitr aur eidul azhaa ke dino mein . aur do tarah se kapdey lapetney se roka hai. eik yun ke koi puri tarah se kapdey mein aisey lipat jaey ke koi uzu bhi us se bahir na rahey . aur dusri soorat yun ke apney ooper kapda lapet kar is tarah baithey ke eik janib se sharmgaah ko nanga kar dey . aur do waqt mein Namaz padhney se bhi mana farmaya hai yani namaze-Fajr aur namaze-Asr ke baad."
2418,"Abu-Murra maula Umme-Hani se riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath unke walid Hazrat Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey to unhoney dono ko khana pesh kiya aur kaha ke khao. Abdullah ne kaha : main rozey se hun. to Amr ne kaha : khao , in dino ke baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein iftaar ka hukm diya kartey they aur rozon se mana farmatey they. Janab Malik ne kaha : is se murad tashreeq ke din hain."
2419,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''  Arfa ke din (naween zul-hijja) nahar ka din (daswin zul-hijja, qurbani ka din) aur ayyaame tashreeq ham ehle-Islam ke eid ke dinon (din) hain. ye khaney aur peeney ke din hain.''"
2420,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs Jumey ka roza na rakhey magar ye ke is se pehley eik din roza rakhey ya eik din baad.''"
2421,"Janab Abdullah bin Basar Salma ki behan Samaa (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haftey ke din ka roza na rakho, siwaye un dinon (dinon) ke jin mein tum par ye farz hon. haftey ke din agar tumhen angoor ki shaakh ka chhilka muyassar aaye ya kisi darkht ki lakdi to usey hi chabaa lo.'' (apney aap ko be-roza bana lo.) Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ye hadees mansookh hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Abdullah bin Basar, Hamsi hain aur ye hadees mansookh hai. isko Hazrat Juweriya ki hadees ne (jo aagey aa rahi hai) mansookh kar diya hai."
2422,Hazrat Juweriya binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke (eik baar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke din unke yahan tashrif laye jabkey ye roze se thin. aapney daryaft farmaya : ''kya tum ne kal  (jumeraat ko) roza rakha tha?'' kehney lagin ke nahin. farmaya : ''kya kal (haftey) ko roza rakho gi?'' kehney lagin ke nahin. farmaya : ''to iftaar kar do.''
2423,Imam ibne-Shahab Zohri ke mutalliq aata hai ke un se jab ye zikr kiya jata ke haftey ke din ka roza rakhney se mana kiya gaya hai to wo kehtey : ye hadees Himsi hai.
2424,Imam Auzaai ne kaha : main eik muddat tak is riwayat ko chhupaey raha. yani mazkura baala hadees Abdullah bin Basar jo ke haftey ke din roza rakhney ke baarey mein hai yahan tak ke maine dekha ke mashhoor ho gaee hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Imam Malik ne isko ''jhoot'' kaha hai.
2425,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap rozey kis tarah rakhtey hain? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski baat se naraz ho gaey. jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye soorate haal dekhi to boley : ham Allah taala ke Rab honey, Islam ke deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Nabi honey par razi hain, ham Allah ki panah chahtey hain ke wo ham par naraz ho ya uska Rasool. aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) apni ye baat musalsal dohraatey rahey yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ghussa zaayel (khatm) ho gaya. phir (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo aadmi kaisa hai jo hamesha hi rozey se rehta ho? aapney farmaya : ''usney roza rakha na iftaar kiya.'' Musaddad ke alfaz they : (لم يصم ولم يفطر - - - - - - - - - या ما صام ولا أفطر) ye shak Ghelaan ko hua hai. (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo aadmi kaisa hai jo do din roza rakhey aur eik din iftaar karey? aapney farmaya : ''kya bhala kisi ko iski taqat bhi hai?'' Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur wo aadmi kaisa hai jo eik din roza rakhey aur eik din iftaar karey? aapney farmaya : ''ye Hazrat Dawud Alehissalam ka roza hai.'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur wo aadmi kaisa hai jo eik din roza rakhey aur do din iftaar karey? aapney farmaya : ''mera ji chahta hai ke mujhey iski taqat di jati.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen din har mahiney mein aur Ramazan se Ramazan tak, (har Ramazan mein purey rozey rakhna) yehi ''Rozatud Dahar'' hai. (sada rozey se rehna hai.) aur Arfa ka roza ; main Allah se umeed rakhta hun ke wo isey eik saal guzishta (pichhle) aur eik saal aainda ka kaffara bana dega. ... . aur aashoora mohrram ka roza . ... . main Allah se umeed rakhta hun ke wo isey guzishta eik saal ka kaffara bana dega.''"
2426,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se us riwayat mein marwi (bayan) hai (Moosaa bin-Ismail ne) mazeed kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! somwaar aur Jumerat ke rozey ke baarey mein aap kya farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : ''is roz meri wiladat hui aur isi mein mujh par Quran nazil kiya gaya.'' (somwaar (peer) ke din.)
2427,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh se miley aur farmaya : ''mujhey bataya gaya hai ke tum kehtey ho : main raat bhar qiyam aur din ko roza hi rakha karunga?'' maine kaha : haan aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine aisa kaha hai. aapney farmaya : ''(raat ko) qiyam karo aur aaram bhi karo, rozey rakho aur iftaar bhi karo (balke) her mahiney mein teen rozey rakha karo, ye ''Rozatud Dahar'' (sada rozey se rehna hai) ki manind hongey.'' (goya zamana bhar rozey rakhey) . maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main is se ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aapney farmaya : ''eik din roza rakh kar do din iftaar kar liya karo.'' maine kaha : main is se ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. farmaya : ''to eik din roza rakha karo aur eik din iftaar kar liya karo, ye rozey rakhney ki moatadil soorat hai aur ye siyaame Dawud (Dawud (Aleh.) ke roze) hai.'' maine kaha : main is se ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aapney farmaya : ''is se badh kar kuchh afzal nahin.''"
2428,"Hazrat Mujeeba Al Bahaliya‬ (Raziallahu anha) apney walid ya chacha se riwayat karti hain ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya. phir eik saal ke baad (dobara) aaya to uski haalat aur kaiyfiyat badli hui thi. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aapney mujhey pehchaana nahin? aapney farmaya : ''tum kon ho?'' usney kaha : main wohi Baahli hun jo pichhley saal aaya tha. aapney puchha : ''tumhari haalat is tarah ghair kyon ho rahi hai, halanke tum achhey bhaley they?'' kehney laga : jab se main aap ke paas se gaya hun maine ye mamool bana liya hai ke bas raat hi ko khana khata hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne apney aap ko azab mein kyon dal rakha hai? '' phir farmaya : ''maahe sabr (Ramazan) ke rozey rakha karo aur phir har mahiney eik roza.'' usney kaha : mujhey mazeed ki ijazat dijiye , yaqinan main taqat rakhta hun. aapney farmaya : ''do din rozey rakho.'' usney kaha : mujhey ziyada ki ijazat dijiye, aapney farmaya : ''teen din rakh liya karo.'' usney kaha : merey liye ziyada kijiye . aapney farmaya : ''hurmat ke mahinon mein rozey rakho aur chhod do, hurmat ke mahinon mein rozey rakho aur chhod do, hurmat ke mahinon mein rozey rakho aur chhod do.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen ungliyon se ishara farmaya. pehley inko band kiya phir khol diya."
2429,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se afzal rozey maahe Ramazan ke baad, Allah ke mahiney mohrram ke rozey hain, aur sab se afzal Namaz farzon ke baad raat ki Namaz hai. ''Qutaiba bin Saeed ne (شهر) ka lafz istimal nahin kiya, balke sirf (Ramazan) kaha."
2430,Usman bin Hakeem kehtey hain ke maine Saeed bin Jubair se rajab ke rozey ke mutalliq sawal kiya to unhoney kaha : mujhey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne khabar di hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rozey rakha kartey to ham kehtey : ab nahin chhoden gey aur kabhi chhod detey to ham kehtey : ab nahin rakhengey.
2431,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke rozey rakhney ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Shoban ka mahina sab se ziyada pasand tha phir aap isey (goya) Ramazan hi se mila detey they.
2432,"Ubaidullah bin Muslim Qarshi apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, kehtey hain ke Siyaame-Dahar (hamesha rozey rakhney) ke mutalliq maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kiya ya kisi aur ne puchha to aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba tumharey ghar walon ka tum par haq hai, Ramazan mein rozey rakho aur uskey sath waley mahiney mein (shawwaal mein) aur her buddh aur Jumerat ko (bhi) to is tarah tum zamane bhar rozey rakhney waley hogey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : (raawi hadees Ubaidullah bin Muslim ke naam mein) Zaid bin Hubaab Ukuli ne Ubaidullah bin Musa ki taeed ki hai aur Abu Nuaim ne mukhalifat ki hai. (baaz Muslim bin Ubaidullah kehtey hain aur kuchh ne Muslim bin Abdullah kaha hai.)"
2433,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jisney Ramazan ke rozey rakhey, phir uskey baad shawwaal mein chhe rozey rakhey to usney goya zamana bhar rozey rakhey.''"
2434,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rozey rakhna shuru kar detey to ham samajhtey ke ab nahin chhoden gey aur jab chhod detey to ham samajhtey ke ab nahin rakhengey. maine nahin dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ramazan ke ilawa kisi mahiney ke purey rozey rakhey hon aur aap Shoban ke ilawa kisi aur mahiney mein ziyada rozey na rakhtey they.
2435,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq bayan kartey hain jaisey ke mazkura baala hadees Aaisha mein guzra hai. aur is mein is qadr ziyada hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Shoban mein bahut kam naagha farmatey they balke (goya) sara Shoban hi rozey rakhtey they.
2436,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke ghulam ne bayan kiya ke wo Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath unka maal leney ke liye wadi Quraa ki taraf gaya. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) somwaar aur Jumerat ka roza rakha kartey they. ghulam ne un se puchha : aap somwaar aur Jumerat ka roza kyon rakhtey hain, halanke aap badi umr ke boodhey ho gaey hain? to unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) somwaar aur Jumerat ka roza rakha kartey they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uskey mutalliq puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''somwaar aur Jumerat ko bandon ke aamaal (Allah ke huzur) pesh kiye jatey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hisham dustwaai ne Yahya se aur usney umr bin Abi Hukm se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
2437,"Ummahaatul Momineen mein se eik ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zul-hijja ke (pehley) no din , aashoora mohrram, har mahiney mein teen din aur har mahiney ke pehley somwaar aur Jumerat ko roza rakha kartey they."
2438,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ko koi nek amal kisi din mein is qadr pasandida nahin hai jitna ke un dino mein pasandida aur mehboob hota hai.'' yani zul-hijja ke pehley das dinon mein. Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya jihade fi-sabee-li-llah bhi nahin? aapney farmaya : ''nahin, jihade-fi-sabee-lillah bhi nahin magar jo koi shakhs apni jaan aur maal lekar nikla ho aur phir kuchh wapis na laya ho.''"
2439,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ushra zil-hijja mein kabhi bhi rozey se nahin dekha.
2440,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke Arfa ke roz Arafat mein roza rakha jaey.
2441,"Hazrat Umme-Fazal binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Arfa ke roz unke yahan kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rozey ke baarey mein ikhtilaf kiya, kuchh ne kaha : aap rozey se hain aur kuchh ne kaha aap rozey se nahin hain. chunanche maine aap ki khidmat mein doodh ka eik piyala bhej diya, jabke aap Arfa ke maidan mein apney oont par Sawar waquf farmaai huey they, to aapney wo nosh (pee) farma liya . (aur is tarah maloom ho gaya ke aapney roza nahin rakha hai.)"
2442,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Aashoora (daswin mohrram) ke din aisa tha ke ehale Quraish Islam se pehley iska roza rakha kartey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi nabuwat se pehley ye roza rakhtey they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina munawwara tashrif laye to aapney is din ka roza rakha aur musalmanon ko bhi uska hukm diya. isliye jab Ramazan farz hua to wohi fariza ho gaya aur Aashoora chhod diya gaya , jo chahta rakh leta aur jo chahta na rakhta."
2443,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Islam se pehley ham daswin mohrram ko roza rakha kartey they. jab Ramazan ka hukm nazil hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Allah ke dino mein se eik din hai jo chahey iska roza rakh ley aur jo chahey chhod dey.''
2444,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Madina munawwara tashrif laye to dekha ke yahood Aashoora ka roza rakhtey hain. un se iskey baarey mein puchha gaya , to unhoney kaha : ye din wo hai ke jis mein Allah taala ne Musa Alehissalam ko Firon par ghalib farmaya tha, aur ham iski tazeem mein roza rakhtey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham tumhari nisbat Musa Alehissalam se ziyada qarib hain'' aur is din ke rozey ka hukm irshad farmaya."
2445,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aashoora ka roza rakha aur hamein bhi uska hukm diya, to Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! is din ki yahood aur Nasara tazeem kartey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aglaa saal aaeyga to ham naween taareekh ka  (bhi) roza rakhengey.'' magar aglaa saal na aaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee."
2446,"Hakam bin Aaraj bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap masjide haram main apni chadar ka takiya banaey huey they. maine un se Aashooraaye mohram ke rozey ke mutalliq poochha. aapney farmaya : ''jab tum mohrram ka chaand dekho to shumar karo, jab naween taareekh ho to roza rakho.'' maine kaha : kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi roza rakha kartey they? unhoney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi roza rakha kartey they."
2447,Abdur-Rehman bin Muslima apney chacha se riwayat kartey hain ke qabeela Aslam ke log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey to aapney un se puchha : ''kya tum ne aaj ka roza rakha hai? '' unhoney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''to baqiya din ko bataur roze ke pura karo aur iski qaza karna. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : is se murad Aashoora ka din tha.
2448,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''Allah taala ke nazdik sab se ziyada pasandida rozey , Hazrat Dawud Alehissalam ke hain, aur sab se pasandida Namaz , Allah taala ke yahan Dawud Alehissalam ki Namaz hai, wo aadhi raat sotay , phir tihai raat qiyam kartey aur phir iska chhata hissey sotay they, aur wo eik din iftaar aur eik din roza rakha kartey they.''"
2449,"ibne Milhaan Qaisi (Abdul-Malik bin Qatada) apney walid (Qatada bin Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham se farmaya kartey they ke ham beez ke dinon mein yani tehra , chaudah aur pandarah taareekh ke rozey rakha karen. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye rozey aisey hain goya sarey zamaney ke rozey.''"
2450,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har mahiney ki ibtida (shuruat) mein teen din rozey rakha kartey they.
2451,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mahiney mein teen rozey rakha kartey they. ( pehley ( somwaar aur Jumerat ko aur agley haftey mein) doosrey ( somwaar ko .'' (is tarah kul teen rozey ho jatey hain.)
2452,"Hanida Khuzaae apni walida se bayan kartey hain, unka kehna hai ke main ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur un se rozon ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey irshad farmaya kartey they ke main her mahiney mein teen rozey rakh liya karun. un mein pehla somwaar ka ho aur (doosra) Jumerat ka ."
2453,Muaza (Adwiya) kehti hain ke maine ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her mahiney mein teen rozey rakha kartey they? unhoney kaha : haan! maine kaha : mahiney ki kin taareekhon ya dino mein rozey rakha kartey they? unhoney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) taareekhon ya dino ki parwa na kartey they. (koi khas dinon muqarrar na they jab chahtey roza rakh liya kartey. (
2454,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Fajr se pehley rozey ki niyat na ki to uska roza durust na hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ye riwayat Imam Leis aur Is-haq bin Hazim ne bhi Abdullah bin Ubai Bakr se usi ke misl marfooan riwayat ki hai aur Maamer, zubaidi, ibne-Uena aur Yunus al-Ela Zohri ke wastey Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se mauqoofan riwayat kartey hain."
2455,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab merey yahan tashrif latey to daryaft farmatey : ''kya tumharey yahan koi khana hai? ''jab ham kehtey ke nahin hai, to aap farmatey : ''main roza rakh leta hun. '' Wakee ne mazeed bayan kya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik doosrey moqe par hamarey paas tashrif laye . ham ne arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamen hees (eik khas arbi tuaam) ka hadiya bheja gaya hai jo ham ne aap ke liye sanbhaal rakha hai. aapney farmaya : ''udhar ley aao.'' Talha ne wazahat ki ke aapney subh ko rozey ki niyat ki thi magar iftaar kar liya."
2456,"Hazrat Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Fateh Makka ke din Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) tashrif laeyn aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baain taraf beth gaeen aur Umme- Hani (Raziallahu anha) aap ki daain taraf thin. bayan karti hain ke khaadima eik bartan lekar aai, us mein mashrub tha, usney wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko diya to aapney us mein se nosh farmaya aur phir Umme-Hani ko dey diya to unhoney bhi us se pi liya aur bolen : aey Allah ke Rasool! maine roza rakha hua tha aur tod liya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''kya ye qaza ka roza tha?'' unhoney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''agar ye nafli tha to koi harj nahin.''"
2457,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo bayan karti hain ke mujhey aur Hafsa ko koi khana hadiya bheja gaya jabkey ham ne roza rakha hua tha, pas ham ne roza tod liya . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur ham ne un se arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamen hadiya diya gaya tha aur hamara khaney ko dil chaha to ham ne roza iftaar kar liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi harj nahin, uski bajaey eik roza rakh lena.'' abu-Saeed bin al-Eirabi kehtey hain ke ye riwayat Sabit nahin hai."
2458,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat ko munasib nahin ke shohar mojud ho to uski ijazat ke baghair roza rakhey magar ye ke Ramazan ke rozey hun. aur aisey hi munasib nahin ke shohar mojud ho to uski ijazat ke baghair kisi ko ghar mein aaney dey.''"
2459,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik khatoon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui jabkey ham bhi aap ke paas hi they. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! mera shohar Safwan bin muattal jab main Namaz padhti hun to mujhey maarta hai aur jab roza rakhti hun to tudwa deta hai aur khud Fajr ki Namaz Suraj chadhey padhta hai. Safwan bhi wahin they. chunanche aapney un se jo kuch aurat ne kaha tha uskey baarey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! uska ye kehna ke jab main Namaz padhti hun to ye maarta hai. ye darasal do do suraten padhti hai aur maine usko us (lambi) qirat se roka hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar eik surat ki qirat ho to bhi logon ko kafi hai. '' aur uska ye kehna ke ye mera roza tudwa deta hai to uski haalat ye hai ke ye rozey hi rakhey jati hai aur main jawan aadmi hun, sabr nahin kar sakta to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us roz farmaya : ''koi aurat apney shohar ki ijazat ke baghair roza na rakhey.'' aur uska ye kehna ke main Suraj chadhey Namaz padhta hun, to haqeeqat ye hai ke hamara gharaana is baat mein maroof hai aur ham log Suraj nikalney se pehley uth hi nahin saktey. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab jaaga karo to Namaz padh liya karo. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Hammad bin Salma ne Humaid ya Sabit sey, unhoney abi-al-Mutwakkil se bayan kya hai."
2460,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko khaney ki dawat miley to chahiye ke qubul kar ley , agar rozey se na ho to khana kha ley aur agar roza rakha hua ho to (majlis mein hazir ho aur ghar walon ke liye) dua karey.'' Hisham bin Hassaan ne wazahat ki ke is hadees mein ''Salat'' ke maani dua karna hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Hafs bin Ghiyas ne bhi Hisham se riwayat kya hai."
2461,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko khaney mein bulaya jaey aur usney roza rakha hua ho to keh dey ke main rozey se hun.''"
2462,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramazanul-mubarak ke aakhiri das dinon mein aetikaf kya kartey they, aakhir hayaat tak aap ka ye mamool raha, aap ke baad phir aap ki pak biviyan bhi aetikaf betha karti thin ."
2463,Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramazan ka aakhiri ashra aetikaf farmaya kartey they. eik saal aap aetikaf na beth sakey to agley saal aapney bees raat tak aetikaf farmaya.
2464,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aetikaf ka irada farmatey to Fajr ki Namaz padh kar apney aetikaf key hujrey mein dakhil ho jatey. eik baar aapney Ramazan ke aakhiri das dinon mein aetikaf ka irada farmaya aur hujra bananey ka hukm diya to wo bana diya gaya jab maine ye dekha to maine keh diya ke mera khema bhi laga diya jaey. chunanche wo laga diya gaya aur phir deegar azwaaj Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhi) dekha dekhi ( khemey laganey ko kaha . chunanche wo laga diye gaey . aapney namaze-Fajr ke baad khemon ko dekha to farmaya : ''ye kya hai, bhala ye neki ka qasad kar rahi hain?'' chunanche aapney apney hujrey ke mutalliq farmaya aur usey khol diya gaya, us par pak biviyon ne bhi apney apney khemey khulwaa liye . phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna ye aetikaf shawwaal ke pehley ashrey tak muakhkhar (deley) farma diya. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : is hadees ko ibn Is-haq aur Auzaai ne Yahya bin Saeed se usi tarah riwayat kya hai jabke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne Yahya bin Saeed se riwayat kya to kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shawwaal ke bees din aetikaf kya."
2465,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramazan ka aakhiri ashra aetikaf farmaya kartey they. Naafe kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah ne mujhey masjide-nabawi mein wo jagah dikhlaai jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf farmaya kartey they.
2466,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her Ramazan ke aakhiri das din aetikaf farmaya kartey they. chunanche jis saal aap ka wisaal hua aapney bees din aetikaf farmaya.
2467,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf ke doran mein apna sar Mubarak meri taraf jhuka detey aur main us mein kanghi kar deti aur aap qazaey-hajat ke liye hi ghar mein tashrif laya kartey they.
2468,ibne-Shahab Zohri b-waasta Urwa aur Umra Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat karti hain. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain aur aisey hi Yunus ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya hai. aur kisi ne bhi (عروہ  an (an)  عمرہ ( ki sanad mein Malik ki mutaabiat nahin ki hai. Maamer aur Ziyad bin Saad waghera) زهري عن  Urwa an (an) عائشة ( ki sanad se riwayat kartey hain.
2469,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein aetikaf mein hotey , aap hujrey mein se apna sar meri taraf kar detey aur main aap ka sar dho deti . Musaddad ke alfaz hain : main aap ki kanghi kar deti jabkey main haaiza hoti ."
2470,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf mein they aur main raat ke waqt aap ki ziyaarat ke liye hazir hui . main aap se baaten karti rahi , phir main wapis aaney ke liye uthi to aap bhi mujhey wapis chhodney ke liye khadey ho gaey jabkey meri rihaaish Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke ehatey mein thi. to ( hamarey paas sey) do Ansari guzrey , jab unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to wo jaldi jaldi chalney lagey , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : '' ruk jao ! ye merey sath ( meri ehliya ( Safiya binte-Huyi hai.'' un dono ne kaha : Subhanallah , aey Allah ke Rasool ! (aap ko kisi qism ki wazahat kerney ki zarurat hi nahin) aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba shetan insan ke jism mein aisey chalta hai jaisey khoon , mujhey andesha hua ke kahin wo tumharey dilon mein kuch dal na dey .'' ya farmaya : '' burai na dal dey .''"
2471,"Shuaib , Zohri se unki sanad se ye riwayat bayan kartey hain. ... ( Hazrat Safiya bayan karti hain ke) jab aap masjid ke darwazey ke qarib pahunchey jo ke Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar ke darwazey ke paas tha to aap ke paas se do aadmi guzrey . aur mazkura baala ( hadees (ke ham maana bayan kya."
2472,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf key dinon mein mareez ke paas se guzartey aur apni raah chaltey jatey aur uska haal ahwaal poochhtey magar us gharz se uski taraf mudte na they. aur ibne-Esa ne kaha ke Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf ki haalat mein mareez ki iyaadat kar letey they.
2473,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : moatakif ke liye sunnat ye hai ke mareez ki iyaadat ko na jaey, janaazey mein shareek na ho, aurat se mas na karey aur na us se mubashrat ( sohbat ( karey aur kisi intehai zaroori kaam ke baghair masjid se na nikley . aur rozey ke baghair aetikaf nahin aur masjid Jaame ke ilawa kahen aetikaf nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq ke ilawa kisi ne '' ( السنة ( '' ke lafz nahin kahey. aur unhoney usey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka qol qarar diya hai."
2474,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ayyaame-jahiliyat mein ye nazar maani thi ke Kaaba main eik raat ya din ka aetikaf karunga. pas unhoney uskey mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney farmaya : '' aetikaf karo aur roza ( bhi) rakho.''
2475,Abdullah bin budail ne ( yehi riwayat ( apni sanad se usi ki manind riwayat ki . us mein izafa hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) aetikaf mein they ke logon ne yakayak takbir buland ki. unhoney puchha : aey Abdullah (ibne-Umar)! ye kya hai? unhoney bataya ke Hawazin ke qaidiyon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne azad kar diya hai. unhoney kaha : to us londi ko bhi (jo Saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas thi ( unke sath chhod do.
2476,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaj se eik ne aapke sath aetikaf kya. usey zardi maael ya surkh sa khoon aata tha. (istihaza ki wajeh sey) to ham kabhi uskey nichey lagan bhi rakh diya kartey they aur wo Namaz padha karti thin.
